<%- include('partials/header', { title: 'About Us' }) %>

<main>
  <!-- About Hero -->
  <section class="about-hero section-light">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Your Guides</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">We are Brazilian women who want to share our homeland with you—not as tour operators, but as friends.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Our Story -->
  <section class="section section-white">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="about-story">
        <div class="about-story-text">
          <h2>Our Story</h2>
          <p>We found ourselves drawn to a particular calling: to serve as guides and companions for women venturing into Brazil, helping them discover not merely the postcard version of this vast country but its deeper rhythms and textures.</p>
          <p>With nearly two decades of experience in international media production, we've spent our careers bridging cultures—working across the UK, United States, China, UAE, and throughout Latin America. We know what it means to make people feel at home in unfamiliar places, to navigate complexity with grace, and to create experiences that resonate.</p>
          <p>But more than our professional backgrounds, what we bring is our deep love for Brazil and our desire to share it authentically. We want to introduce you to the places we love, the people who have shaped us, and the moments that remind us why we call this place home.</p>
          <p class="signature">— Raquel & friends</p>

          <div class="credentials">
            <h3>Background</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>Based in Niterói, Rio de Janeiro, Brazil</li>
              <li>Nearly 20 years in international media production</li>
              <li>Experience across UK, US, China, UAE, Panama, Ecuador, Brazil</li>
              <li>Lead Producer at Barn Media</li>
              <li>Fluent in Portuguese, English, and Spanish</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="about-image">
          <img src="/images/Raquel.png" alt="Raquel - Your Guide" class="about-photo">
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Philosophy -->
  <section class="section section-sand">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Our Philosophy</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="philosophy">
        <div class="philosophy-item">
          <h3>Connection Over Content</h3>
          <p>We're not interested in checking boxes or collecting Instagram moments. We care about genuine human connection—with the places we visit, the people we meet, and each other. The best travel memories are rarely the famous landmarks; they're the unexpected conversations, the spontaneous detours, the moments when something shifts inside you.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="philosophy-item">
          <h3>Slow & Intentional</h3>
          <p>Six nights is enough time to settle in, to let go of the rushing, to actually arrive somewhere. We don't pack itineraries with activities. We leave room for wandering, for long lunches, for the serendipity that only happens when you're not in a hurry.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="philosophy-item">
          <h3>Women Holding Space for Women</h3>
          <p>There's something particular about how women travel together—the conversations that unfold, the trust that builds, the way vulnerability becomes a doorway to deeper connection. We honor that. We create environments where women can be fully themselves, wherever they are in their journey.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="section section-light">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header" style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
        <h2>Want to Know More?</h2>
        <p>Explore what a journey with us looks like, or reach out to start a conversation.</p>
        <div style="margin-top: 2rem; display: flex; gap: 1rem; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap;">
          <a href="/experience" class="btn btn-primary">The Experience</a>
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-outline">Contact Us</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
